title: Abigail Philips - If No Be For You
seo_description:
This is a worship medley where, the music minister drills us about her love and dependence on God. The song simply says ; if not of God, she would not be where she is today. Indeed, God deserves all our worship , he deserves it all because he is the author and finisher of our faith.

If not by the mercies and grace of God, you wouldn't be anywhere today.
